---
title: Italian Pork Meatballs & Bacon Sauce with Garlicky Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: How many meatballs are too many? The answer is you can never have enough of these pork meatballs! Served with all-time
favourites like garlic mash and steamed veggies, and all topped off with a bacon-loaded sauce, it doesn’t get any better than this.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cc25d4ccfe394f89a54b26-b61cbdd4.jpeg
